<dl id="n12048k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12048k">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12048k"> 48(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> mass on druid altar</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">the priests, who escaped the sword, are hunted to bogs and mountains; and there surrounded by a faithful people, <mark>with a huge rock for an altar</mark>, and the heavens for a canopy, the &ldquo;tremendous mystery of Redemption&rdquo; is offered to the Almighty <small> Very Rev. Dean Kinane, <a name="TKSP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#TKSP"><cite title="source">St. Patrick: his life, his heroic virtues, his labours, and the fruits of his labours</cite></a>, (ed. unknown) 262</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
